{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777005225478,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_wwnhz7YsvWClK2ntTvteyiV8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\apps\\mobile\\capacitor.config.ts","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\apps\\mobile\\capacitor.config.ts</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: import type { CapacitorConfig } from \"@capacitor/cli\";\n2: \n3: const config: CapacitorConfig = {\n4:   appId: \"chat.soft.app\",\n5:   appName: \"Chat Soft\",\n6:   webDir: \"dist\",\n7:   server: {\n8:     androidScheme: \"http\",\n9:     cleartext: true\n10:   }\n11: };\n12: \n13: export default config;\n\n(End of file - total 13 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"import type { CapacitorConfig } from \"@capacitor/cli\";\n\nconst config: CapacitorConfig = {\n  appId: \"chat.soft.app\",\n  appName: \"Chat Soft\",\n  webDir: \"dist\",\n  server: {\n    androidScheme: \"http\",\n    cleartext: true\n  }\n};\n\nexport default config;","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\apps\\mobile\\capacitor.config.ts","time":{"start":1777005225426,"end":1777005225477}},"id":"prt_dbdc3e5c1001T9FDe1hd9kn1zE","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbdc3cc32001n5lqwAIA09HENU"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777005225489,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_IQUHbUfg6K2kth3tVJ7MkYX1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\architecture\\v1_tech_stack.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\architecture\\v1_tech_stack.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Chat Soft V1 技术选型建议\n2: \n3: ## 1. 选型目标\n4: \n5: V1 的目标不是一步到位做到最强，而是：\n6: \n7: - 快速跑通\n8: - 跨端可维护\n9: - 易于后续扩展\n10: - 能给 AI 留接口\n11: \n12: ## 2. 推荐技术栈\n13: \n14: ## 2.1 Android 客户端\n15: \n16: - 语言：Kotlin\n17: - UI：Jetpack Compose\n18: - 本地存储：Room + SQLite\n19: - 网络：Ktor Client 或 OkHttp + WebSocket\n20: - 音频录制：MediaRecorder / AudioRecord\n21: - 音频播放：ExoPlayer 或 MediaPlayer\n22: \n23: 选择理由：\n24: \n25: - 安卓原生支持最好\n26: - 后续做录音、通知、前台服务更自然\n27: \n28: ## 2.2 Windows 客户端\n29: \n30: 推荐：\n31: \n32: - 桌面壳：Tauri\n33: - 前端：React\n34: - 本地服务层：Rust\n35: - 本地数据库：SQLite\n36: - 本地 API：Rust 内置 HTTP + WebSocket + CLI\n37: \n38: 选择理由：\n39: \n40: - Windows 打包相对轻\n41: - Rust 适合做本地 Agent 和接口层\n42: - 后续对接 AI、本地自动化和系统权限更灵活\n43: \n44: 备选：\n45: \n46: - Electron + Node.js\n47: \n48: 不作为首选原因：\n49: \n50: - 资源占用更高\n51: - 后续本地服务能力虽然也能做，但整体更重\n52: \n53: ## 2.3 服务端\n54: \n55: - 语言：TypeScript\n56: - 运行时：Node.js\n57: - 框架：NestJS 或 Fastify\n58: - 实时链路：WebSocket\n59: - 数据库：PostgreSQL\n60: - 缓存/队列：Redis\n61: - 媒体存储：本机磁盘目录\n62: \n63: 推荐优先：\n64: \n65: - `Node.js + Fastify + ws + PostgreSQL + Redis`\n66: \n67: 理由：\n68: \n69: - V1 开发速度快\n70: - 实时通信和后台任务足够\n71: - 后期若要拆服务也容易\n72: \n73: ## 2.4 部署\n74: \n75: - 云服务器：香港轻量应用服务器\n76: - 系统：Ubuntu 22.04 LTS\n77: - 部署方式：Docker Compose\n78: \n79: ## 3. V1 模块拆分\n80: \n81: ### 3.1 server\n82: \n83: - auth-service\n84: - device-service\n85: - chat-service\n86: - sync-service\n87: - media-service\n88: - notification-service\n89: \n90: ### 3.2 windows-app\n91: \n92: - desktop-ui\n93: - desktop-core\n94: - local-agent\n95: \n96: ### 3.3 android-app\n97: \n98: - android-ui\n99: - android-core\n100: - sync-engine\n101: \n102: ### 3.4 shared\n103: \n104: - api-schema\n105: - message-model\n106: - event-model\n107: \n108: ## 4. 为什么不建议 V1 直接上 WebRTC\n109: \n110: V1 先只做文本和语音消息，不做实时通话。\n111: \n112: 原因：\n113: \n114: - WebRTC 会引入 STUN/TURN、编解码、弱网问题\n115: - 会明显拖慢第一版验证速度\n116: - 当前第一目标是把消息链路和媒体链路跑稳\n117: \n118: ## 5. 为什么服务端用中心化消息模型\n119: \n120: - 最容易做离线补收\n121: - 最容易做多设备同步\n122: - 最容易观察延迟和问题\n123: - 最容易给 AI 提供稳定接口\n124: \n125: ## 6. V1 电脑端 AI 接口建议\n126: \n127: ### HTTP\n128: \n129: - `POST /api/messages/text`\n130: - `POST /api/messages/voice`\n131: - `GET /api/messages/recent`\n132: - `GET /api/messages/search`\n133: \n134: ### WebSocket\n135: \n136: - `message.created`\n137: - `message.updated`\n138: - `sync.completed`\n139: \n140: ### CLI\n141: \n142: - `chatsoft send-text`\n143: - `chatsoft send-voice`\n144: - `chatsoft recent`\n145: - `chatsoft search`\n146: \n147: ## 7. 关键风险\n148: \n149: - 香港节点到内地移动网络的链路波动\n150: - 语音消息上传下载体验\n151: - 多设备同步状态一致性\n152: - 本地 API 的权限控制\n153: \n154: ## 8. V1 技术结论\n155: \n156: 推荐方案：\n157: \n158: - Android：Kotlin + Compose\n159: - Windows：Tauri + Rust + React\n160: - Server：Node.js + Fastify + PostgreSQL + Redis\n161: - Deploy：香港轻量服务器 + Docker Compose\n\n(End of file - total 161 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Chat Soft V1 技术选型建议\n\n## 1. 选型目标\n\nV1 的目标不是一步到位做到最强，而是：\n\n- 快速跑通\n- 跨端可维护\n- 易于后续扩展\n- 能给 AI 留接口\n\n## 2. 推荐技术栈\n\n## 2.1 Android 客户端\n\n- 语言：Kotlin\n- UI：Jetpack Compose\n- 本地存储：Room + SQLite\n- 网络：Ktor Client 或 OkHttp + WebSocket\n- 音频录制：MediaRecorder / AudioRecord","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\architecture\\v1_tech_stack.md","time":{"start":1777005225435,"end":1777005225488}},"id":"prt_dbdc3e5d3001M9ainSnXRsQOUo","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbdc3cc32001n5lqwAIA09HENU"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777005225501,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_vEph2LKNXFTabvHvtwRuA6tk","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\plan\\development_plan.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\plan\\development_plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Chat Soft 开发计划\n2: \n3: ## 1. 总体阶段\n4: \n5: ### 阶段 0：方案落地\n6: \n7: - 完成正式需求文档\n8: - 完成总体架构设计\n9: - 锁定技术栈\n10: - 购买并准备服务器\n11: \n12: ### 阶段 1：后端骨架\n13: \n14: - 初始化服务端工程\n15: - 建立 PostgreSQL / Redis / Docker Compose\n16: - 完成设备注册与配对\n17: - 完成 WebSocket 基础链路\n18: \n19: ### 阶段 2：V1 文本消息\n20: \n21: - 文本消息发送\n22: - 文本消息接收\n23: - 消息状态流转\n24: - 本地落库\n25: - 服务端补收\n26: \n27: ### 阶段 3：V1 语音消息\n28: \n29: - 安卓录音\n30: - Windows 语音消息收发\n31: - 音频文件上传下载\n32: - 进度播放\n33: \n34: ### 阶段 4：多设备同步与通知\n35: \n36: - 消息同步游标\n37: - 离线补收\n38: - 安卓通知\n39: - Windows 通知\n40: \n41: ### 阶段 5：电脑端 AI 接口\n42: \n43: - 本地 HTTP API\n44: - 本地 WebSocket\n45: - CLI\n46: \n47: ## 2. V1 验收标准\n48: \n49: - 文本消息跨网稳定可用\n50: - 语音消息跨网稳定可用\n51: - 设备离线后可补收消息\n52: - Windows 端 API 可被本地 AI 调用\n53: \n54: ## 3. 当前建议的开发顺序\n55: \n56: 1. 服务器与数据库先跑通\n57: 2. Windows 客户端先做最小原型\n58: 3. 安卓客户端再接入\n59: 4. 文本消息优先\n60: 5. 语音消息第二\n61: 6. AI 接口第三\n62: \n63: ## 4. 当前待办\n64: \n65: - 购买香港服务器\n66: - 初始化 monorepo\n67: - 搭建 server 原型\n68: - 搭建 desktop 原型\n69: - 搭建 android 原型\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Chat Soft 开发计划\n\n## 1. 总体阶段\n\n### 阶段 0：方案落地\n\n- 完成正式需求文档\n- 完成总体架构设计\n- 锁定技术栈\n- 购买并准备服务器\n\n### 阶段 1：后端骨架\n\n- 初始化服务端工程\n- 建立 PostgreSQL / Redis / Docker Compose\n- 完成设备注册与配对\n- 完成 WebSocket 基础链路\n\n### 阶段 2：V1 文本消息\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\plan\\development_plan.md","time":{"start":1777005225446,"end":1777005225498}},"id":"prt_dbdc3e5dc001lh7x58FSRQ7A01","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbdc3cc32001n5lqwAIA09HENU"}}
